variety of constraints generates a set of candidate optimal\nstrategies. Stochastic Dynamic Programming is finally implemented to choose the\nbest strategy considering competitors, whose motion is generated by the MC\nsimulator. Our approach, validated on data from a real stint of race, allows to\nsignificantly reduce the lap time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 20:33:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-21"}
