istent with other shell-model calculations suggesting a quenched\nvalue of $g_{\\rm A}$. Using this value of $g_{\\rm A}$, predictions for the\ntransition half-lives were derived.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 21:55:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2022 13:41:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
