dings add to our understanding of gas adsorption and\ndiffusion behaviors in the vicinity of PIM-1/silica interfaces, which are\nunobtainable in experimental studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 07:15:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Jun 2022 06:43:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-07"}
