 $s^{1/3}$-dependence of the transport rate, but fails to\ncapture the latter's superimposed grain size dependence. This hints at a lack\nof understanding of the transport rate physics and calls for future studies on\nthis issue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 15:39:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Apr 2022 11:08:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2022 09:29:51 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 19:00:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-23"}
