\nenhanced Helium to predict the Helium content of three M31 clusters. We discuss\nwhat this can tell us about their mass and fraction of first generation stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 15:45:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
