namics not possible today when\nimplemented together with X-ray multi-projection imaging, and ii) enhancing the\nvolumetric information and capabilities of X-ray stereoscopic imaging in\nmedical applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 04:16:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-03"}
